        "name": "TaskHub API",
        "description": "Postman collection for TaskHub REST API — Authentication & Task Management.\n\nAvailable query parameters for GET /api/tasks:\n- `priority` (string): Filter by priority level. Accepted: low, moderate, high\n- `status` (string): Filter by completion status. Accepted: pending, completed\n- `deadline` (string): Filter tasks with approaching deadline. Accepted: approaching\n- `sort` (string): Sort order. Accepted: newest (default), oldest, priority, deadline\n\ncreated by risyandi.com - 2026",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
